SUMMARY:ICBMT 2026
LOCATION:Busan\, Korea
DESCRIPTION:主辦單位：ICBMT\n地點：Busan\, Korea\n學會頁面：ht
 tps://www.tbmt.org.tw/publicUI/D/D10402.aspx?arg=8DEBB1369733B6A071\n\n---
  活動內容 ---\nICBMT 2026 Overview\n[Summary]\nTitle\nThe 10th Annual 
 International Congress of Blood and Marrow Transplantation (ICBMT 2026)\nD
 ates\nSeptember 17 (Thursday) &ndash\; September 19 (Saturday)\, 2026\nVen
 ue\nBEXCO\, Busan\, Korea\nTheme\nNext Horizon: Pioneering the Breaking th
 roughs in HSCT and Cell therapy\nHosted by\nThe Korean Society of Blood an
 d Marrow Transplantation\nPrograms\nPlenary Sessions\, Presidential Sympos
 ium\, Scientific Sessions\, Education Sessions\,\nEast Asia Collaborative 
 Session\, Joint Symposiums\, Oral & Poster Presentations\,\nLuncheon Sympo
 siums\, Nursing Session\, Debate Session\, Exhibition\n- Program at a Glan
 ce: https://icbmt.co.kr/program/\nHomepage\nhttps://icbmt.or.kr/\n[Abstrac
 t Submission]\n- Abstract submission deadline: June 12 (Fri)\, 2026\n- Pre
 sentation type: Oral or Poster Presentation\n- Abstract main topics:\nMyel
 oid Malignancies\n(AML\, MDS\, MPN)\nAcute Lymphoblastic Leukemia\nBone Ma
 rrow Failure\nCellular & Gene Therapy\nBlood and Marrow Collection and Pro
 cessing\nInfectious Complications\nLymphoma\nPost-transplant Complications
  (Non-infectious)\nMyeloma\nNursing/Allied Health\nPediatric Hematology/On
 cology\nTransplantation Specific Topics\nStem Cell Biology\nOthers\n-\n- S
 ubmit your abstract: https://icbmt.co.kr/abstract/\n[Award Opportunities]\
 n- The ICBMT 2026 Organizing Committee will offer various awards which wil
 l be given to presenters whose abstracts have been accepted. Submit your o
 utstanding abstracts for a chance to win awards!\n* The candidate must be 
 the presenting author of an accepted abstract\, register\, and attend the 
 congress in-person.\nOutstanding Oral Presentation Awards\nTravel Awards\n
 (Overseas presenters only)\nOverseas Contribution Awards\n(Overseas presen
 ters only)\nKRW 1\,000\,000\nKRW 2\,000\,000\nKRW 700\,000\n[Registration]
 \n- Early-bird registration deadline: July 31 (Fri)\, 2026\n- Find out mor
 e & register: https://icbmt.co.kr/registration/index_eng.php\nEarly Regist
 ration Rate\n(By July 31\, 2026)\nPre-Registration Rate\n(By August 28\, 2
 026)\nOnsite Rate\n(September 17-19\, 2025)\nUSD 100\nUSD 150\nUSD 200\nGa
 la Dinner\nUSD 10\n[Inquiries]\nICBMT 2026 Secretariat\nTel: +82-02-566-60
 31\nFax: +82-2-566-6087\nEmail: icbmt@icbmt.or.kr
